addPublicVariableEventHandler 
Behavior: global 
Game: Armed Assault (1.09) 
Description: If the EH detects a change via publicVariable on the given variable 
, code will be executed. 
The following arguments are transferred to the code:  
_this select 0: variable name 
_this select 1: new variable value 
Syntax:  
 varName addPublicVariableEventHandler code 
Parameters: 
varName: String 
code: Code 
Return Value: 
 Nothing